metadata.name: The Seeker
metadata.description:
The Seeker appears when the dark descends. 
Some describe it as a tall, thin figure shrouded in a dark cloak while others describe it as a floating specter, drifting through the night with a sinister air. 
No one knows for sure where it comes from, but legend has it that it will take away all the sorrow and pain of anyone it meets. 
You just need to be willing to walk side by side with the Seeker for a little while in the darkness.
